woven fabriclike materials used in feminine hygiene and adult incontinence products wipes and other airlaid applications its specialty papers business unit is engaged in the sale of papers for carbonless and other forms envelopes book publishing and engineered products such as papers for highspeed ink jet printing office specialty products greeting cards postal and other specialty applications more from reuters » officers and directors dante c parrini chairman of the board chief executive officer age  bio  compensation   reuters trading activity  yahoo finance john p jacunski chief financial officer executive vice president business unit president  specialty papers age  bio  compensation   reuters trading activity  yahoo finance christopher w astley senior vice president  business unit president advanced airlaid materials age  bio  compensation   reuters timothy r hess senior vice president  business unit president specialty papers age  bio  compensation   reuters martin rapp senior vice president  business unit president composite fibers age  bio  compensation   reuters joseph j zakutney chief information officer vice president bio  compensation   reuters david c elder vice president  finance chief accounting officer age  bio  compensation   reuters kent k matsumoto vice president general counsel corporate secretary age  bio  compensation   reuters samuel l hillard vice president  corporate development  strategy age  bio  compensation   reuters kathleen a dahlberg lead independent director age  bio  compensation   reuters full list on reuters » google finance beta available in hong kong  canada  us  china  ukinformation is provided as is and solely for informational purposes not for trading purposes or advice and may be delayedto see all exchange delays please see disclaimer google  google home  blog  help  report a problem  privacy policy  terms of service glatfelter  wikipedia glatfelter from wikipedia the free encyclopedia jump to navigation search for the aster