nt initiative encouraging farmers to plant more trees and prevent soil erosion in  glatfelter launched a tree farm managed for the growing of sustainable forest crops in pennsylvania and maryland glatfelter’s previous president and ceo george henry glatfelter ii is the greatgreat grandson of the founder philip henry glatfelter  who also founded york ice company which became york heating and air conditioning glatfelters work with sustainable tea packaging was highlighted in the september  issue of the tea  coffee trade journal productsedit airlaid materials book publishing carbonless forms composite fibers composite laminates engineered products envelope and converting papers food and beverage papers metallized films and papers specialty uncoated papers technical specialties referencesedit  a b c d e httpwwwglatfeltercomfilesaboutusinvestorrelationsannualreportpdf  httpwwwglatfeltercomfilesaboutusinvestorrelationsqearningsreleasepdf  lipper mark  paper people progress the story of the ph glatfelter company of spring grove pennsylvania englewood cliffs nj prenticehall p  isbn    glatfelter book papers specialty papers engineered paper products home glatfeltercom retrieved    tea packaging for impact and sustainability by katrina ávila munichiello tea  coffee trade journal external linksedit benway stuart glatfelters paper discount business week archived from the original on  retrieved  july   retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitleglatfelteroldid categories companies listed on the new york stock exchangecompanies based in york county pennsylvaniacompanies established in pulp and paper companies of the united statesyork pennsylvania establishments in pennsylvaniahidden categories wikipedia articles with possible conflicts of interest from july articles lacking reliable references from july all articles lacking reliable references navigation menu personal tools not logged intalkcontributionscreate accountlog in namespaces article talk variants views read edit v