turers metallized products that are used in label packaging liner gift wrap and other consumer product applications composite laminate papers for use in production of decorative laminate furniture and flooring applications and special paper products which are used in electrical energy storage transport and transmission wipes and other highlyengineered fiberbased applications its advanced airlaid materials business unit supplies absorbent cellulosebased airlaid nonwoven materials that are used to manufacture consumer products such as feminine hygiene specialty wipe adult incontinence home care and other consumer products the company’s specialty papers business unit offers carbonless and noncarbonless forms papers for credit card receipts multipart forms security papers and other enduser applications engineered products for high speed ink jet printing office specialty products greeting cards and other niche specialty applications envelope and converting papers for transactional and direct mail envelopes and book publishing papers for the production of hardbound books and other book publishing needs p h glatfelter company markets its products directly as well as through wholesale paper merchants brokers and agents the company was founded in  and is headquartered in york pennsylvania detailed description  south george streetsuite york pa united statesfounded in  employees phone  wwwglatfeltercom key executives for p h glatfelter company mr dante c parrini chairman chief executive officer and president age  total annual compensation k mr john p jacunski chief financial officer and executive vice president age  total annual compensation k mr martin rapp senior vice president and business unit president of composite fibers age  total annual compensation k mr christopher w astley senior vice president and business unit president of advanced airlaid materials age  total annual compensation k mr kent k matsumoto vice president general counsel and corporate secretary age  total annual compensation k compensation as of fiscal year  p h glatfelter company key developments glatfelter appoints tina m moylan as director specialty inkjet products jun   glatfelter announced that tina m moylan joined its specialty papers business unit as director specialty inkjet products reporting to david dickerhoof vice president sales  marketing effective june  in this new role tina will bring significant industry experience and will be responsible for leading the development of glatfelters product portfolio sales channels and growth strategies for inkjet printable substrates tina brings  years of experience in the paper industry including  years at glatfelter in a variety of technical and product development roles most recently tinas career focused on sales and marketing of inkjet substrates p h glatfelter company presents at houlihan lokey  global industrials conference may  pm may   p h glatfelter company presents at houlihan lokey  global industrials conference may  pm venue hilton midtown new york  th avenue new york ny  united states speakers john p jacunski chief financial officer and executive vice president glatfelter declares cash dividend payable on august   may   glatfelter announced that its board of directors declared a  per share cash dividend on its outstanding common stock the dividend is payable on august   to shareholders of record as of the close of business on july   similar private companies by industry company name region ab lumber company llc united states a roof trusses ltd united states a b massa paper corp united states alrt corporation united states ami forest industries inc united states recent private companies transactions typedate target no transactions available in the past  months request profile update   the information and data displayed in this profile are created and managed by sp global market intelligence a division of sp global bloombergcom does not create or control the content for inquiries please contact sp global 