elebrate glatfelter’s th anniversary watch the “squawk box” interview featuring dante parrini a global supplier of specialty paper and engineered products glatfelter delivers more than quality paper products going beyond paper is our promise to our customers based on over a century and a half of experience and technical expertise and supported by new bestinclass processes glatfelter on clear channel in celebration of glatfelter’s th anniversary chairman and ceo dante parrini was interviewed by michael yorba on ‘the trader’s network show’ listen to the  minute interview here quality products our products have expanded from highquality book publishing papers and envelopes to an array of highly technical products like tea bags postage stamps and playing cards view our product directory innovative approaches our people devise effective creative solutions to your paper challenges our process and product innovations result from glatfelter people questioning the norm customer service with global reach our team approach to customer service allows our experts to be your dedicated resource and with locations in north america europe and asia we have a global presence to support you worldwide sustainability we conduct business using practices that protect and enhance the environmental social and economic resources needed by future generations to enjoy a life equal to or greater than our own   learn more read our corporate overview to learn more or read our press releases for the latest information   glatfelter  terms of use  privacy policy  suppliers  site map  feedback  rss feeds california transparency act disclosure headquarters   glatfelter suite   south george street york pa  usa   contact us related resources   policies  certifications our safe harbor policy  kb pdf we selfcertify compliance with follow us   p h glatfelter  glatfelter paper company cutting  jobs  traders log in email password remember forgot password  become a member for free sign up sign up new membersig