ur careersuccess built on valuesglatfelter cultureglobal total rewards   home  careers create your own success story at glatfelter since  our employees—glatfelter people—have defined our success working together to create innovative quality products for millions of people the world over as an equal opportunity and affirmative action employer glatfelter employs over  people worldwide in a variety of professional fields including paper manufacturing mechanical engineering sales  marketing customer service information technology finance and administration at glatfelter you’ll be part of a strong and growing multinational company continuing our success story as well as your own glatfelter employees are people who are passionate about finding innovative solutions for our customers believe in doing whatever it takes to get the job done never settle for less than the best and consistently strive to exceed expectations in turn we offer a rewarding sustainable work environment based on a culture of values glatfelter needs people like you and we’re pleased that you are interested in a career with us what do glatfelter people say about working here get an inside look at the glatfelter career experience from our employees—glatfelter people—who are living it today what’s kept us successful since  there’s a reason why we’ve remained a leader for over a centuryandahalf shared common values that benefit employees and customers alike—values lived every day by people like you how does glatfelter offer a sustainable work situation glatfelter views sustainability as more than an environmental initiative it’s a way of life shared by glatfelter people and lived every day in the workplace what makes glatfelter’s global total rewards package so attractive glatfelter puts people first by designing total rewards packages to attract retain motivate and reward the employees who are crucial to the success of our business   did you know glatfelter’s  locations include facilities in the us canada europe and asia with over  employees worldwide — with more than  employees in pennsylvania alone during the great depression despite unemployment as high as  at times glatfelter never laid off a single employee glatfelter was one of the industry’s pioneers in employee communications employee safety programs and wellness initiatives glatfelter developed the first sustainably managed tree farms in pennsylvania and maryland in the early s glatfelter partnered with the commonwealth of pennsylvania to build lake marburg and help create codorus state park as an outdoor recreation area for all to enjoy glatfelter began as a single paper mill in spring grove pa valued at  and today is a  billion dollar global industry leader   glatfelter  terms of use  privacy policy  suppliers  site map  feedback  rss feeds california transparency act disclosure glatfelter on cnbc   watch cnbcs “squawk box” interview featuring dante parrini the glatfelter story   this minute video depicts glatfelters journey of transformation that began in  and continues today glatfelters journey of transformation literature   glatfelter people in motion  mb pdf our brand startswith you  mb pdf enhancing your everyday life  kb pdf code of conduct mb pdf learn how glatfelter builds a better tomorrow  mb pdf information feeds   career opportunities view all feeds follow us   search for jobs at glatfelter location   all locations athens oh  athens oh baloi facility  baloi philippines berlin office  berlin germany caerphilly facility  caerphilly united kingdom chillicothe oh facility  chillicothe oh corporate headquarters york pa  york pa corporate jobs ohio  ohio corporate jobs spring grove pa  spring grove pa corporate jobs worldwide  worldwide delmar md wood yard  delmar md dresden facility  dresden germany falkenhagen facility  falkenhagen germany fremont ohio facility  fremont ohio gainesville ga sales office  gainesville ga gatineau qc facility  gatineau canada gernsbach facility  gernsbach germany lydn