ployees to find new manufacturing positions at the ohio facility  c the york dispatch york pa visit the york dispatch york pa at wwwyorkdispatchcom distributed by tribune content agency llc tribune content agency source regional news  latest news on p h glatfelter co p p h glatfelter  glatfelter paper company cutting  jobs  glatfelter p h co  other events financial statements and exhibits form k  glatfelter  announces cost reduction measures in its specialty papers business   glatfelter  to report earnings on august st  global specialty paper market  most popular players  domtar mondi stor  p h glatfelter co  exdividend day  p h glatfelter  glatfelter p h co submission of matters to a vote of security h  glatfelter  bolsters specialty papers inkjet sales team  glatfelter  to present at the deutsche bank global industrials and materials su  glatfelter  to present at the houlihan lokey th annual global industrials con more news news from seekingalpha  p h glatfelter company glt presents at deutsche bank th annual global in  p h glatfelter glt presents at houlihan lokeyth annual global industria  glatfelter declares  dividend  consumer  top gainers  losers as o   pm  glatfelters glt ceo dante parrini on q  results  earnings call trans financials  sales    m ebit   m net income   m debt   m yield   pe ratio   pe ratio   ev  sales  x ev  sales  x capitalization  m more financials chart p h glatfelter co duration  auto  months  months  months  months  year  years  years  years max period  day week fullscreen chart technical analysis trends p h glatfelter co short termmidtermlong termtrendsbullishbearishbearish technical analysis income statement evolution please enable javascript in your browsers settings to use dynamic charts more financials consensus sell buy mean consensus outperform number of analysts  average target price   spread  average target  consensus details eps revisions please enable javascript in your browsers settings to use dynamic charts more estimates r