w  full description p h glatfelter company incorporated on december   is a manufacturer of specialty papers and fiberbased engineered materials the company operates through three business units composite fibers advanced airlaid materials and specialty papers its composite fibers business unit is engaged in the sale of singleserve tea and coffee filtration papers nonwoven wallcovering materials metallized papers composite laminates papers and various technically special papers including substrates for electrical applications its advanced airlaid materials is engaged in the sale of airlaid nonwoven fabriclike materials used in feminine hygiene and adult incontinence products wipes and other airlaid applications its specialty papers business unit is engaged in the sale of papers for carbonless and other forms envelopes book publishing and engineered products such as papers for highspeed ink jet printing office specialty products greeting cards packaging casting release transfer playing card postal and other specialty applications the company owns and operates manufacturing facilities located in pennsylvania ohio canada germany the united kingdom france and the philippinescomposite fibersthe companys composite fibers business unit serves customers across the globe and focuses on valueadded products in various markets such as food and beverage which includes filtration paper primarily used for singleserve coffee and tea products wallcovering including base materials used by wallpaper manufacturers metallized which includes products used in the labels packaging liners gift wrap and other consumer product applications composite laminates which includes paper used in production of decorative laminates furniture and flooring applications and technical specialties which includes a diverse line of special paper products used in electrical energy storage transport and transmission wipes other home and hygiene products and other fiberbased applications the composite fibers business unit consists of four paper making facilities germany france and england a nonwoven wall cover base mill germany metallizing operations wales and germany and a pulp mill the philippinesadvanced airlaid materialsthe companys advanced airlaid materials business unit is a global supplier of absorbent cellulosebased airlaid nonwoven materials primarily used to manufacture consumer products for global end user markets its products include feminine hygiene specialty wipes adult incontinence home care and other consumer products advanced airlaid materials serves various customers including consumer product companies as well as privatelabel converters for feminine hygiene adult incontinence and specialty wipes products the advanced airlaid materials business unit operates facilities in falkenhagen germany and gatineau canada as of december   the falkenhagen location operated three multibonded production lines and three singlelane festooners as of december   the gatineau location consisted of two airlaid production lines employing multibonded and thermalbonded airlaid technologies and two singlelane festoonersspecialty papersthe companys north americabased specialty papers business unit focuses on producing papers for various markets such as carbonless and noncarbonless forms papers engineered products envelope and converting and book publishing markets the company offers papers for credit card receipts multipart forms security papers and other end user applications in the carbonless and noncarbonless forms market it offers engineered products for high speed ink jet printing office specialty products greeting cards and other specialty applications it offers papers primarily utilized for transactional and direct mail envelopes in the envelope and converting market it also offers papers for the production of highquality hardbound books and other book publishing needsthe company competes with ahlstrom purico mb papeles zhejiang kan technocell neu kaliss goznak schweitzermaudit oi feng ar metallizing torras papel novelis vaassen galileo nanotech wenzhou protec vacuum metallizing co georgiapacific llc fitesa mcairlaids gmbh appvion inc fibria celulose koehler paper mitsubishi paper nekoosa coated products asia pulp and paper co international paper domtar corp packaging corp sappi limited north pacific paper and resolute forest » full overview of glt company address p h glatfelter co  s george st ste york   pa    p  company web links home page officers  directors name compensation dante parrini  john jacunski  christopher astley  timothy hess  martin rapp  » more officers  directors p h glatfelter co news briefglatfelter announces cost reduction measures in its specialty papers business unit jul   briefglatfelter reports q earnings per share  may   briefglatfelter sets quarterly dividend of  per share feb   » more glt news related topics stocksstock screenerbasic materialspaper products